A G4S van was robbed while collecting money from a Total garage in Tasbet Park, Emalahleni, Mpumalanga.Police spokesperson Brigadier Leonard Hlathi said while the guard was in the station&#8217;s office collecting money, two males entered the garage shop and pretended to be customers.After collecting the money and heading back to the G4S truck, the guard was followed by two men who threatened him with firearms and took the money and the guard&#8217;s gun.